text.tspan: Based on the expert assessments and index by the Bertelsmann Transformation Index (2022), weighted by countries'
populations. It combines information on the extent of political participation, the rule of law, stable democratic
institutions, political and social integration, and a capable state. It ranges from 1 to 10 (most democratic).
Data source: Bertelsmann Transformation Index (2022); HYDE (2017); Gapminder (2022); UN (2022)
